## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the potential biases inherent in historical documentation. Many justifications for slavery were constructed within the context of their time and may not fully capture the complexities of the arguments used. Additionally, the reliance on online sources may exclude certain scholarly works not available in digital format. Further research into primary historical documents and scholarly analyses would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the justifications for slavery.